These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, tea
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, august, march
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, aquamarine, light-blue
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, azalea, begonia
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, techno, salsa
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, subway, train
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
5. the person who growsazalea is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is between the fan of funk and the person who's birthday is in august##2
8. the person driving the bus is on the right of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | tea     | milk      | fanta      |
| Birthday          | august   | july   | march       |
| Color   | light-blue | ebony | aquamarine    |
| Flower   | begonia  | iris    | azalea    |
| Music-Genre           | techno    | salsa    | funk |
| Transport     | subway  | train     | bus        |

