.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, tea
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, photographer, accountant
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, jazz, rock
House: ranch-style, craftsman, wooden
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, rat
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing, camping
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the security-guard##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the fan of rock##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the craftsman house##1
6. the accountant is between the wooden house and the person drinking tea##2
7. the fan of jazz is between the fan of rock and the owner of the rat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | fanta     | cola        | tea      |
| Job          | photographer    | accountant       | security-guard  |
| Music-Genre   | rock     | jazz | house    |
| House   | wooden | ranch-style   | craftsman    |
| Pet           | goat      | chinchilla  | rat      |
| Hobby         | camping    | rock-climbing      | puzzles |

