6. the nigerian is on the right of the colombian##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
8. the victorian house is between the alhambra-smoker and the person who likes blood-red##2
9. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3       |
