The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, august, january
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, time-travel, western
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, aristoff, chaman
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, writing, skydiving
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, rowing, swimming
There 3 different types of food: pumpkin, artichoke, lemon
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person eating lemon is between the person eating pumpkin and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
8. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |     3      |
| Birthday      | january     | may   | august      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | western  | superhero  |
| Cigar   | vegafina       | aristoff  | chaman        |
| Hobby           | skydiving       | writing   | chess |
| Sport         | rowing      | swimming | climbing   |
| Food     | artichoke   | lemon     | pumpkin |

 